OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Live results as
OL,4,Cthe battle for Hampshire gets underway
OL,6,FCounting is underway across Hampshire,
OL,7,FPortsmouth, Southampton and on the
OL,8,FIsle of Wight, after hundreds of
OL,9,Fthousands cast their votes in the 2026
OL,10,Flocal elections.
OL,12,FThe Conservatives are hoping to keep
OL,13,Fcontrol of Hampshire County Council,
OL,14,Fwhilst both Reform UK and the Liberal
OL,15,FDemocrats are hoping to make gains.
OL,17,FIt's one of the biggest councils in
OL,18,Fthe country, serving nearly 1.5million
OL,19,Fpeople, and managing a budget of more
OL,20,Fthan #3billion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
