OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Live results as
OL,4,Cthe battle for Hampshire gets underway
OL,6,FUse our interactive map to see the
OL,7,Fresults of each seat in the Hampshire
OL,8,FCounty Council elections.
OL,10,FEyes are also on the Labour-run
OL,11,FSouthampton City Council, and
OL,12,FPortsmouth City Council, which is
OL,13,Fcurrently under no overall control.
OL,15,FWhilst on the Isle of Wight, every
OL,16,Fseat is up for grabs. All parties are
OL,17,Ftrying to win seats on the island,
OL,18,Fwhich is currently under no overall
OL,19,Fcontrol.
