OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Live results as
OL,4,Cthe battle for Hampshire gets underway
OL,6,FElections should have taken place last
OL,7,Fyear, but they were delayed because of
OL,8,Flocal government reorganisation.
OL,10,FUse our interactive map to see the
OL,11,Foverall results for borough and
OL,12,Fdistrict councils in Hampshire.
OL,14,FThe majority of smaller local councils
OL,15,Fhave held elections in Hampshire too.
OL,17,FOnly Test Valley, New Forest and East
OL,18,FHampshire were not up for election
OL,19,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
