OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Live results as
OL,4,Cthe battle for Hampshire gets underway
OL,6,FIn Gosport, Reform UK are hoping to
OL,7,Fmake gains from the Liberal Democrats.
OL,8,FWhilst in Fareham, the Tories are
OL,9,Fhoping to keep control of the council,
OL,10,Fwhere they have 32 councillors.
OL,12,FIn Eastleigh, the Liberal Democrats
OL,13,Fare hoping to maintain their grip on
OL,14,Fthe authority, which they have run for
OL,15,Fmore than 30 years.
OL,17,FUse our interactive map to see the
OL,18,Foverall results for unitary councils
OL,19,Fin Hampshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
