OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Live results as
OL,4,Cthe battle for Hampshire gets underway
OL,6,FMeanwhile on Portsmouth City Council,
OL,7,Fwhere a third of the seats are up for
OL,8,Fgrabs, parties are hoping they can get
OL,9,Fenough votes to take it out of no
OL,10,Foverall control.
OL,12,FNext year people will, if government
OL,13,Freforms go ahead, be voting for new
OL,14,F'super' authorities, as part of
OL,15,Freorganisation plans.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
