OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Live results as
OL,4,Cthe battle for Hampshire gets underway
OL,6,FThese votes could well be the last for
OL,7,Fthe councils in their current forms,
OL,8,Fwith new South East and South West
OL,9,FHampshire authorities, along with a
OL,10,FMid Hampshire and North Hampshire
OL,11,Fcouncils being formed in 2028.
OL,13,FThe Isle of Wight however will keep
OL,14,Fits council, but will fall under the
OL,15,Fnew Hampshire mayor, who is due to be
OL,16,Felected later this decade.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
